07/20

Brand Equity Assistant ...




臺北市信義區








 


傑太日煙國際股份有限公司




11-30人應徵




							
								2017~2018 One-year Internship - Brand Equity Assistant



Assist brand owners in the Brand Equity team for the following areas:
- KA listing / SRA document development / Product picture submission / Barcode procurement / CH side panel procurement / Chinese name list maintenance / Mock up preparation (agency contact only) / Procurement and payment process / Other ad-hoc tasks.
Potential extended areas include:
- Closely cooperate with other department to analyze consumer behavior and look for insight through researches.
- Work with cross-functional stakeholders to support project rollout and performance tracking.
- Ongoing monitoring and analysis of sales trends, product quality, market data and competitor activity.

Perform other assignments or special projects as requested by supervisor; develop own capability to step up to higher responsibility role.


- Undergraduate junior/senior year, or first year of graduate school (Candidates must be above age 20 and enrolled in an University studying on a undergraduate or graduate degree)
- Able to work two full days at least per week 


- Fluent English (or a good English capability) is preferred 
- Familiar with Microsoft applications and operations
- A good understanding of JTI company and marketing standards in tobacco industry is a plus
							
						




07/20

管理部實習生-學生實習




彰化縣大村鄉








 


正新橡膠工業股份有限公司




0-5人應徵




							
								1.協助一般請購及採購作業
2.協助開發新廠商與管理
3.協助採購相關流程與供應商管理
							
						




